descriptions.value: Powerful and reliable, the AK-47 is one of the most popular assault rifles in the world. It is most deadly in short, controlled bursts of fire. It has been given an eclectic mix of hydrographic decals then drip painted. No suicide squad would be complete without it
Sticker: FaZe Clan | Paris 2023, Stone Scales, The Baiter, Supreme Master First Class

High risk and high reward, the infamous AWP is recognizable by its signature report and one-shot, one-kill policy. It has been custom painted using a combination of hydrographics and careful stenciling and detailed with heat-transfer decals. Chase Turner was a great man... you have big shoes to fill – The Phoenix and The Initiate, Part 1

As expensive as it is powerful, the Desert Eagle is an iconic pistol that is difficult to master but surprisingly accurate at long range. Dragons have been laser-etched onto the slide and grip. I'm a big fan of your work Yukako, we should talk... -Huxley, The Competition
Sticker: Headshot Guarantee, Team Kinguin | Cologne 2015

An ideal pistol for the Terrorist on the move, the Tec-9 is lethal in close quarters and features a high magazine capacity. It has been custom painted with totally radical blue and pink highlights. Available for 4 easy payments of $124.95!
Sticker: Spirit | 2020 RMR

This Music Kit will replace all of the music in the game and is shareable with anyone you are playing with. It also includes an MVP Anthem that plays for everyone in the match when you are MVP.

The Music Kit replaces the following music:
- Main Menu
- Round Start and End
- Map Objective
- Ten Second Warning
- Death Camera
Made especially for those games when you feel... different. Haunt your enemies round after round with the "inhuman" Music Kit from ISOxo.

With a smaller magazine than its unmuffled counterpart, the silenced M4A1 provides quieter shots with less recoil and better accuracy. It has been etched with a basilisk. It's rude to stare, but war isn't the time for pleasantries

A less expensive option among the terrorist-exclusive assault rifles, the Galil AR is a serviceable weapon in medium to long-range combat. It has been painted white and green and detailed with heat-transfer decals. For enough money, Elite Crew will take any cause on as their own

A low-recoil firearm with a high rate of fire, the P250 is a relatively inexpensive choice against armored opponents. It has been custom painted with circular motifs. This one is steeped in tradition and blood
This is a Series 3 collectible pin. It can be displayed on your CS:GO profile.

A cheap option for cash-strapped players, the FAMAS effectively fills the niche between more expensive rifles and the less-effective SMGs. It has been inlaid with gold and nickel and engraved with the image of a jinn. Be careful what you wish for
Sticker: FalleN | Boston 2018, coldzera | Boston 2018

The misunderstood middle child of the SMG family, the UMP45's small magazine is the only drawback to an otherwise versatile close-quarters automatic. It has been given a decal of a sabertooth tiger skull Every predator eventually meets their end

A fan favorite from Counter-Strike Source, the Silenced USP Pistol has a detachable silencer that gives shots less recoil while suppressing attention-getting noise. It has been custom painted with pink accents over a silver and black base. Keep your head

The SSG08 bolt-action is a low-damage but very cost-effective sniper rifle, making it a smart choice for early-round long-range marksmanship. It has been custom painted with manic pink, blue, and purple drawings on a black base. H@@HH@H@H@HA!!
Versatile but expensive, the German-made MP7 SMG is the perfect choice for high-impact close-range combat. It has been covered in white logo decals over a red and black hydrographic. Space for rent
Sticker: Entry Fragger, VINI | Antwerp 2022, Please Return To, Little Mischief
or an Exceedingly Rare Special Item!

A fully automatic variant of the CZ75, the CZ75-Auto is the ideal short-term choice for turning the tables and gaining your opponents weapon. But with very little ammo in the magazine, strong trigger discipline is required. It has heat-transferred decals applied to a white and green base. For a better tomorrow
Name Tag: ''☯受委屈本身并不算什 么除非你继续记得它''

A low-recoil firearm with a high rate of fire, the P250 is a relatively inexpensive choice against armored opponents. A custom paint job inspired by video cassette packaging from the 1990s has been applied. Check the tape
Sticker: My Little Friend, Backstab, TACO | Berlin 2019, Mahjong Rooster

The R8 Revolver delivers a highly accurate and powerful round at the expense of a lengthy trigger-pull. Firing rapidly by fanning the hammer may be the best option when point-blank stopping power is required. It has been custom painted to resemble a very ripe banana. Catch them slipping
Sticker: Miami Wave Rider, Backstab, TACO | Berlin 2019, Mahjong Rooster
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.
*Stats for this item will reset when used in Steam Trading or Community Market

The CT-exclusive Mag-7 delivers a devastating amount of damage at close range. Its rapid magazine-style reloads make it a great tactical choice. It has been covered in monochromatic silver and black designs. You either have it or you don't

The terrorist-exclusive SG553 is a premium scoped alternative to the AK47 for effective long-range engagement. It has been hand painted with a blue and grey design and finished with orange accents. A ScyTech procurement

Powerful and accurate, the AUG scoped assault rifle compensates for its long reload times with low spread and a high rate of fire. It has been custom painted using dark fantasy and horror as inspiration. "Like a moth to a flame"

Manufactured in Switzerland, the cutting-edge MP9 SMG is an ergonomic polymer weapon favored by private security firms. It has been custom painted with dynamic, angular shapes and a stylized spider. It's not the first bite that kills you, it's the 29 that come after

The Glock 18 is a serviceable first-round pistol that works best against unarmored opponents and is capable of firing three-round bursts. It has been given a hydrographic of Bobby the Mischievous Weasel. Don't mess with Bobby. Just because he's cute, doesn't mean he doesn't bite

Firing two large-mag Berettas at once will lower accuracy and increase load times. On the bright side, you'll get to fire two large-mag Berettas at once. It has dragons laser-etched on the slide and barrel. Marian was always cooler than Sylvia

Highly accurate and armor-piercing, the pricy Five-Seven is a slow-loader that compensates with a generous 20-round magazine and forgiving recoil. It has been custom painted with a graphic design in violet and black. How will you rule?

The CT-exclusive Mag-7 delivers a devastating amount of damage at close range. Its rapid magazine-style reloads make it a great tactical choice. It has been painted using an urban Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic over a metallic base coat.

Essentially a box that bullets come out of, the MAC-10 SMG boasts a high rate of fire, with poor spread accuracy and high recoil as trade-offs. It has been painted with a chrome base coat and candied in transparent silver anodized effect paint. There is beauty in simplicity - Franz Kriegeld, Phoenix Tactician

Essentially a box that bullets come out of, the MAC-10 SMG boasts a high rate of fire, with poor spread accuracy and high recoil as trade-offs. It has been custom painted to appear as if you are looking into the back of the MAC-10. Custom built
The Nova's rock-bottom price tag makes it a great ambush weapon for a cash-strapped team. It has been custom painted with longships and dragons. It emerged from the fog of war

The Negev is a beast that can keep the enemy at bay with its pin-point supressive fire, provided you have the luxury of time to gain control over it. It has been given a base coat of blue metallic paint then hand-painted with metallic gold swirls and accents. Turn some heads before you take them off
More accurate but less damaging than its AK-47 counterpart, the M4A4 is the full-auto assault rifle of choice for CTs. A black and white circuit board pattern has been applied. At the heart of it all

More accurate but less damaging than its AK-47 counterpart, the M4A4 is the full-auto assault rifle of choice for CTs. It has been painted using a Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic. By the time you're close enough to notice the pixels it's already too late

Highly accurate and armor-piercing, the pricy Five-Seven is a slow-loader that compensates with a generous 20-round magazine and forgiving recoil. It has been painted using a forest camouflage hydrographic. The woods can be a dangerous place... never travel alone
